snippet.title: Nintendo 64 Longplay [029] FIFA Road to World Cup 98
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Let;s qualify for that world cup of 98, and not only that, this version offers you the whole world cup after you beat the qualifications. Played as the great Yugoslavia team, back in this days, that didn;t do much on the real world cup but that;s another story, why not alter the history with these great old; games. No skills involved, but with the powers of rerecording no skills are actually needed to beat this game. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
